{{Infobox person |name = Pery Igel |birth_date = November 27, 1921 |image = Pery Igel.jpg |nationality = Brazilian |occupation = Businessman, second president of [[Ultrapar]] |death_date = {{death-date and age|September 24, 1998|November 27, 1921}} |father = [[Ernesto Igel]] |relatives = [[Daisy Igel]] (sister) }}
'''Pery Igel''' (November 27, 1921 – September 24, 1998) was a Brazilian businessman. Igel was [[Ultrapar|Ultra]]'s second president, succeeding his father and company's founder, [[Ernesto Igel]].
==Biography== Igel was the administrator and second president of Ultra. He took over the company created by his father, [[Ernesto Igel]], in 1959. After two years as president, Igel moved the headquarters from Rio de Janeiro to São Paulo, Brazil.<ref name=DiskBrasilGas>{{cite web |url=http://www.diskbrasilgas.com.br/historia/index.htm|title=História|accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref> Under Pery’s administration, [[Oxiteno]] and Ultracargo were founded, two of the five divisions of Ultra, along with [[Ultragaz]] (first division of Ultra), as well as [[Petróleo Ipiranga|Ipiranga]] and [[Extrafarma]], which were incorporated to the group respectively in 2007 and 2014.
Under his administration, the company created and also dissociated a number of other activities that have stopped being related to Ultra's long-term strategy, such as a domestic appliances retailer (Ultralar), an engineering company (Ultratec), a frozen food organization (Supergel,) and the fertilizer industry (Ultrafértil.)<ref name=EconomiaiG>{{cite web |url=http://economia.ig.com.br/com-acordo-de-acionista-prorrogado-ultra-planejara-seu-futuro-nos-proximos-dois-anos/n1237575355745.html |title=Com acordo de acionista prorrogado,Ultra planejará seu futuro dos próximos dois anos|accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref>
Igel stepped down as CEO in 1981 and appointed Vice President [[Paulo Cunha (businessman)|Paulo Cunha]] to the position. Igel became president of the Ultra's Board of Directors and remained its main [[shareholder]].<ref name=Valor>{{cite web |url=http://www.valor.com.br/sites/default/files/upload_element/22-02_ultrapar_balanco_ok_todos.pdf|title=Ultrapar em 2012 |accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref> Após deixar a presidência executiva, Pery seguiu como presidente do Conselho Administrativo do Ultra e seu principal acionista.<ref name=GoogleNews>{{cite web |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1246&dat=19980926&id=imYyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-rcFAAAAIBAJ&pg=6513,1677535&hl=pt-BR|title=País perde um de seus maiores empresários |accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref>
Before his death in September 1998, Igel transferred the controlling shares of Ultra to his family and to a small group of Ultra executives through the creation of a holding company.<ref name="PacíficoGestãodeRecursos">{{cite web |url=http://www.pagr.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Pacifico-Acoes-1T14.pdf|title=Pacífico Ações |accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref><ref name=Administradores>{{cite web |url=http://www.administradores.com.br/artigos/economia-e-financas/sucessao-empresarial-como-manter-o-negocio-nas-proximas-geracoes/36933/|title=Sucessão empresarial: como manter o negócios nas próximas gerações. |accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref><ref name=UNESP>{{cite web |url=http://geein.fclar.unesp.br/jornais_det.php?codigo=7781|title=Igel faz madeira plástica com reciclados |accessdate=June 2, 2015}}</ref>
